## CSS Implementation Example
```css
.component {
  /* Use design system tokens */
  color: var(--color-primary-600);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: var(--text-base);
  line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  
  /* Use consistent spacing */
  padding: var(--spacing-4);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
  
  /* Accessibility considerations */
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
```

## Design-to-Code Workflow
1. Create designs in appropriate tool (Figma, Adobe XD, etc.)
2. Document component specifications
3. Prepare assets for development
4. Generate design tokens
5. Implement designs with appropriate technology
6. Verify implementation matches design specifications